OL,3,CPrivate prescriptions issue could have
OL,4,Ccost Jersey taxpayers millions
OL,6,FAn issue which saw some private
OL,7,Fpatients in Jersey receiving their
OL,8,Fprescriptions without charge has been
OL,9,Fgoing on for decades rather than just
OL,10,Fa few years, anonymous sources suggest.
OL,12,FThe two anonymous sources told ITV
OL,13,Freporter Alex Spiceley they believe it
OL,14,Fcould have cost the taxpayer millions
OL,15,Fof pounds.
