OL,3,CPrivate prescriptions issue could have
OL,4,Ccost Jersey taxpayers millions
OL,6,FIt follows a Freedom of Information
OL,7,Frequest in October which showed
OL,8,FJersey's government has spent #200,000
OL,9,Fon prescriptions that should have been
OL,10,Fpaid for by 25 private patients on two
OL,11,Fdrugs.
OL,13,FThe Electronic Prescribing and
OL,14,FMedicines Administration (EPMA) system
OL,15,F- brought in at the start of May -
OL,16,Ffirst flagged the issue.
OL,18,FThere are different types of
OL,19,Fprescriptions on the island including:
