OL,3,CPrivate prescriptions issue could have
OL,4,Ccost Jersey taxpayers millions
OL,6,FThe issue is thought to have stemmed
OL,7,Ffrom consultants writing prescriptions
OL,8,Ffor private patients on HCS-branded
OL,9,Fpaper, which should have been taken to
OL,10,Fcommunity or retail pharmacies to be
OL,11,Fcharged.
OL,13,FHowever, some patients - who might not
OL,14,Fhave been aware that they were meant
OL,15,Fto pay - took prescriptions to the
OL,16,Fhospital where the Health Department
OL,17,Ffooted the bill.
