OL,6,FDuring that time, those private
OL,7,Fpatients would have received quicker
OL,8,Faccess to treatment than those on a
OL,9,Fwaiting list.
OL,11,FHealth Minister Deputy Tom Binet
OL,12,Fpreviously said it is unclear how long
OL,13,Fthis has been going but said a full
OL,14,Finvestigation would cost hundreds of
OL,15,Fthousands of pounds and insists that
OL,16,Fthe EPMA system will stop errors from
OL,17,Fhappening in the future.
