OL,3,CPrivate prescriptions issue could have
OL,4,Ccost Jersey taxpayers millions
OL,6,FBut anonymous sources now suggest that
OL,7,Fthe issue has allegedly gone on for
OL,8,Fclose to 30 years, raising concerns
OL,9,Fthat the full cost for the health
OL,10,Fdepartment could be in the millions.
OL,12,FITV News has also seen emails from
OL,13,F2022 that first advised staff to
OL,14,Fcharge for private prescriptions but
OL,15,Fthen backtracked on the decision less
OL,16,Fthan two weeks later.
OL,18,FThe emails were sent by the then
OL,19,FDeputy Chief Pharmacist Debbie
OL,20,FO'Driscoll two years before the EPMA
OL,21,Fsystem flagged the issue.
